title: Extraordinary Trendition 9/30: Joel Embiid, Ray J, 'Rap City', Sen. Blumenthal, NBA, Britney Spears
itunes:title: Extraordinary Trendition 9/30: Joel Embiid, Ray J, 'Rap City', Sen. Blumenthal, NBA, Britney Spears
description:
In this edition of Extraordinary Trendition, Jack and Miles discuss Joel Embiid's comments on Jimmy Butler, Ray J being Brandy's brother, 'Rap City' rising from the ashes, Sen. Blumenthal's question to Facebook, unvaxx'd NBA players facing an uncertain season, and Britney Spears' conservatorship
